    <title>lan-eg</title>
    <url>/2026/04/22/lan-eg/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="lan-eg"><a href="#lan-eg" class="headerlink" title="lan-eg"></a>lan-eg</h1><h2 id="第一篇文章哦"><a href="#第一篇文章哦" class="headerlink" title="第一篇文章哦"></a>第一篇文章哦</h2><h3 id="这个是三级标题"><a href="#这个是三级标题" class="headerlink" title="这个是三级标题"></a>这个是三级标题</h3><span id="more"></span>

<ul>
<li>列表1</li>
<li>列表2<br>  a 字列表哦<br>  b 字列表哈</li>
<li>列表3</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://github.com/lan666-y">github网址</a></p>
<p><em>字体是斜线的</em><br><strong>字体是不是加粗了呢</strong></p>
<p><code>&lt;html&gt;&lt;html&gt;</code></p>
<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>我是标题哦<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>我的内容是引用的哦</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
