  <entry>
    <title>我的第一篇博客文章</title>
    <url>/2026/04/16/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>美化博客</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h1 id="开启首页阅读全文模式，只显示摘要"><a href="#开启首页阅读全文模式，只显示摘要" class="headerlink" title="开启首页阅读全文模式，只显示摘要"></a>开启首页阅读全文模式，只显示摘要</h1><h2 id="config配置"><a href="#config配置" class="headerlink" title="config配置"></a>config配置</h2><figure class="highlight nix"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 必须改成false！关闭自定义description摘要</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">excerpt_description:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 保持true，开启阅读全文按钮</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">read_more_btn:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="加截断符号"><a href="#加截断符号" class="headerlink" title="加截断符号"></a>加截断符号</h2><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 加在文章中要隐藏的文字前面</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- more --&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr>
<h1 id="开启打赏功能"><a href="#开启打赏功能" class="headerlink" title="开启打赏功能"></a>开启打赏功能</h1><h2 id="打开zh-CN文件，修改"><a href="#打开zh-CN文件，修改" class="headerlink" title="打开zh-CN文件，修改"></a>打开zh-CN文件，修改</h2><figure class="highlight autoit"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta"># 文件位置</span></span><br><span class="line">blog\themes\<span class="keyword">next</span>\languages\zh-CN.md</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="/images/reward_config.png" alt="打赏文字修改方式"></p>
<figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta"># 开启打赏方式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">reward:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  wechatpay:</span> <span class="keyword">/images/</span>wechatpay.jpg</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  alipay:</span> <span class="keyword">/images/</span>alipay.jpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h1 id="开启动态背景"><a href="#开启动态背景" class="headerlink" title="开启动态背景"></a>开启动态背景</h1><figure class="highlight nix"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 搜索canvas</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">canvas_ribbon:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="params">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>    <span class="comment"># 总开关：true开启彩带动画，false关闭完全隐藏</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="params">size:</span> <span class="number">300</span>       <span class="comment"># 彩带的宽度大小，数字越大彩带越宽</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="params">alpha:</span> <span class="number">0.6</span>      <span class="comment"># 彩带透明度：0完全透明看不见，1完全不透明实心，0.6半透明刚好好看</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="params">zIndex:</span> <span class="operator">-</span><span class="number">1</span>      <span class="comment"># 层级：-1代表彩带在网页最底层、背景后面，不会挡住文字、按钮、内容</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h1 id="给博客添加fork-github"><a href="#给博客添加fork-github" class="headerlink" title="给博客添加fork github"></a>给博客添加fork github</h1><h2 id="打开网址"><a href="#打开网址" class="headerlink" title="打开网址"></a>打开网址</h2><p><a href="https://tholman.com/github-corners/">github-corners</a><br><img src="/images/corners.png" alt="corners"><br><a href="https://github.blog/news-insights/github-ribbons/">github Ribbons</a><br><img src="/images/ribbons.png" alt="ribbons"></p>
<h2 id="添加corners至右上角"><a href="#添加corners至右上角" class="headerlink" title="添加corners至右上角"></a>添加corners至右上角</h2><h3 id="复制corners配置"><a href="#复制corners配置" class="headerlink" title="复制corners配置"></a>复制corners配置</h3><figure class="highlight axapta"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#打开配置文件，配置文件所在路径</span></span><br><span class="line">\blog\themes\<span class="keyword">next</span>\layout\_layout.njk </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#找到这行，第20行，复制在这行的下一行</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;<span class="keyword">div</span> <span class="keyword">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;headband&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="keyword">div</span>&gt; </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta"># 改为自己github路径</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;https://your-url&quot;</span> <span class="keyword">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;github-corner&quot;</span> <span class="meta">#原本示例链接</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;a href=<span class="string">&quot;https://github.comm/lan666-y&quot;</span> <span class="meta">#自己github地址</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#保存刷新即可</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="/images/corners_fig.png" alt="corners-fig"></p>
<hr>
<h1 id="修改文章内链接样式"><a href="#修改文章内链接样式" class="headerlink" title="修改文章内链接样式"></a>修改文章内链接样式</h1><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 配置文件路径</span><br><span class="line">\blog\themes\next\<span class="selector-tag">source</span>\css\_common\components\post\post-<span class="selector-tag">body</span><span class="selector-class">.styl</span></span><br><span class="line"># 在文件最后加上以下函数</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.post-body</span> <span class="selector-tag">p</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#345</span></span><br><span class="line">  border-bottom: none;</span><br><span class="line">  &amp;<span class="selector-pseudo">:hover</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">color</span>: red;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr>
<h1 id="修改文章底部带-的标签"><a href="#修改文章底部带-的标签" class="headerlink" title="修改文章底部带#的标签"></a>修改文章底部带#的标签</h1><figure class="highlight axapta"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta"># 配置文件路径</span></span><br><span class="line">\blog\themes\<span class="keyword">next</span>\layout\_macro\post.njk</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta"># 增加配置，就会变成google的图标</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;i <span class="keyword">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;fa fa-google&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/i&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="/images/tag_fig.png" alt="tag_fig"></p>
<hr>
<h1 id="增加来必立评论"><a href="#增加来必立评论" class="headerlink" title="增加来必立评论"></a>增加来必立评论</h1><h2 id="配置文件对应代码段"><a href="#配置文件对应代码段" class="headerlink" title="配置文件对应代码段"></a>配置文件对应代码段</h2><ul>
<li>选择默认加载哪个评论系统<br>active后面是空的，代表当前所有评论全部关闭，页面不会显示任何评论！<br>想启用Livere（来必力），改成 active: livere 即可。<figure class="highlight nix"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 多评论系统支持（核心功能：同时装多个评论插件，页面可以互相切换）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Multiple Comment System Support</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">comments:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Available values: tabs | buttons # 评论切换控件样式，二选一：</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># tabs = 标签页横向切换（你现在用的这个，最美观）</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># buttons = 按钮方块切换</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="params">style:</span> tabs</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Choose a comment system to be displayed by default.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Available values: disqus | disqusjs | livere | gitalk | utterances | isso</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 【核心配置】选择页面打开**默认自动加载**哪一个评论系统</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 可选值已经列出来了：disqus | disqusjs | livere | gitalk | utterances | isso</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="params">active:</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Setting `true` means remembering the comment system selected by the visitor.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 功能：是否记住访客上次选的评论插件</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># true = 访客上次切到Gitalk，下次打开文章自动还是Gitalk</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># false = 每次打开文章都强制重置成上面active设置的默认评论</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="params">storage:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Lazyload all comment systems.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 功能：评论懒加载</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># false = 页面打开立刻加载评论（你现在的设置）</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># true = 滚动到文章底部才加载评论（优化首页加载速度，推荐改成true）</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="params">lazyload:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Modify texts or order for any naves, here are some examples.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 自定义每个评论插件：页面显示文字、排序先后顺序</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="params">nav:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#disqus:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#  text: Load Disqus  # 页面上这个按钮显示的文字</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#  order: -1        # 排序优先级，数字越小越靠左排</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#gitalk:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#  order: -2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="livere评论配置"><a href="#livere评论配置" class="headerlink" title="livere评论配置"></a>livere评论配置</h2><figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># LiveRe comments <span class="keyword">system</span></span><br><span class="line"># You can get your uid <span class="keyword">from</span> https:<span class="comment">//livere.com/insight/myCode (General web site)</span></span><br><span class="line">livere_uid: # &lt;your_uid&gt; # 换成实际的uid</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="来必力uid获取"><a href="#来必力uid获取" class="headerlink" title="来必力uid获取"></a>来必力uid获取</h2><p><a href="https://www.livere.com/apply">livere</a><br>安装，首次安装需登录，然后注册新建博客站点，再次验证就可安装，得到uid</p>
<figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 来必力安装代码uid</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;livere-comment <span class="attribute">client-id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;jdeMFmho8Q7pdnjlf1Ff&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/livere-comment&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script <span class="attribute">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;module&quot;</span> <span class="attribute">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://www.livere.org/livere-widget.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>改动：1、active: livere 2、livere_uid: your_uid</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="各评论系统选择"><a href="#各评论系统选择" class="headerlink" title="各评论系统选择"></a>各评论系统选择</h2><p><img src="/images/comment_fig.png" alt="评论系统选择"></p>
<hr>
<h1 id="开启git评论"><a href="#开启git评论" class="headerlink" title="开启git评论"></a>开启git评论</h1><h2 id="原代码段"><a href="#原代码段" class="headerlink" title="原代码段"></a>原代码段</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Gitalk</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># For more information: https://gitalk.github.io</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">gitalk:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">github_id:</span> <span class="comment"># GitHub repo owner</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="comment"># Repository name to store issues</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">client_id:</span> <span class="comment"># GitHub Application Client ID</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">client_secret:</span> <span class="comment"># GitHub Application Client Secret</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">admin_user:</span> <span class="comment"># GitHub repo owner and collaborators, only these guys can initialize gitHub issues</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">distraction_free_mode:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># Facebook-like distraction free mode</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># When the official proxy is not available, you can change it to your own proxy address</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">proxy:</span> <span class="string">https://cors-anywhere.azm.workers.dev/https://github.com/login/oauth/access_token</span> <span class="comment"># This is official proxy address</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Gitalk&#x27;s display language depends on user&#x27;s browser or system environment</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># If you want everyone visiting your site to see a uniform language, you can set a force language value</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Available values: en | es-ES | fr | ru | zh-CN | zh-TW</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">language:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># If you want to customize the content of the initialized Issue, please edit the body parameter.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># For example:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># body: Comments for post $&#123;title&#125;, see $&#123;url&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">body:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="创建"><a href="#创建" class="headerlink" title="创建"></a>创建</h2><ul>
<li>申请 Gitalk 必须的 client_id &#x2F;client_secret<br>Gitalk 需要 GitHub 第三方授权，必须创建&#x2F;注册一个 OAuth App<br><a href="https://github.com/settings/applications/new">OAuth App</a></li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight livecodeserver"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 注册OAuth App页面配置</span></span><br><span class="line">Applacation name <span class="comment">#任意，无须和github名一致</span></span><br><span class="line">Homepage <span class="built_in">URL</span> <span class="comment"># 必须与博客地址一致</span></span><br><span class="line">Application description <span class="comment">#任意，描述词</span></span><br><span class="line">Authorization callback <span class="built_in">URL</span> <span class="comment"># 必须与博客地址一致</span></span><br><span class="line">Enable Device Flow <span class="comment"># 不用勾选</span></span><br><span class="line">Register application <span class="comment">#点击创建，即可获得client_ID和client_secret(密钥)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
